flowchart LR
R[Rupture] --> S[Stop Escalation]
S --> F[Facts]
F --> H[Hear Both Accounts]
H --> A[Allocate Responsibility]
A --> P[Specific Apology]
P --> T[Tangible Repair]
T --> B[Behavior Change]
B --> W[Observation Window]
W --> C{Recurrence?}
C -- No --> CL[Close and Learn]
C -- Yes --> ES[Escalate Tollgate]
